Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 艾尔梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们要去的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅人之间的风评并不怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该是非常地不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会端上难吃的饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅人一去 店家就会关门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子会拿石头扔你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被人说到这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人对那个国家的真面貌充满兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺还真是好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮的国家嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不足以了解居住在此的人们的内心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿或许会成为你日后非常值得回味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永生难忘的国家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:15.72,标题1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,250)\fad(500,100)}「温柔之国」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴沉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 阴沉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旅行者 旅行者来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算滞留几天？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 我想待到后天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎您来到我国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们诚挚地欢迎您的造访
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一个人来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会举国欢迎你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么需要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里肯定是另一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有能留宿的地方 能请你们告诉我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有沐浴设备 最好是价格不太昂贵的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家就是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的伙伴艾尔梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔梅斯你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我父母经营的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请你带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫樱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好听的名宇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何含义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是花名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛开于春天的 粉色漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我朋友总是叫我阴沉鬼来戏弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可言喻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有好久没有外国的客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是我的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了经营旅馆 他们也兼任这附近的观光向导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去准备房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你托我买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买到了比平常还好的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好、好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是麻烦你 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一楼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有大房间空着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能方便艾尔梅斯进入的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否让我做你在这个国家的观光向导？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力以赴地去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 如果你有想去的地方 一定要跟我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉和以往的风评完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也大为惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面左转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要抓紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好照顾吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜托您帮我修枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…明天我也休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:06:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个旅行者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只待到明天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你下午再来一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？樱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿非要好好打理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想去什么地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…若有能了解这个国家历史的地方就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人惊异啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得久还是有好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是历史博物馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 在遥远的国度中有一群遭受迫害与追捕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们造访了四处的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而却没有国家愿意接纳他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后他们历经了漫长的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于森林深处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但森林的恩惠拯救了饥饿的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将这座无人厌恶自己的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为永久安居之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创立了一个新的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我现在伫立于此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立足于这个时代的潮流前端
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解这个国家的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这片土地所满怀着的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从幼时起 就在那儿被传授了历史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都拥有一颗感谢大地恩惠的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能将这个当作礼物收下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个… 这个也请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是犬子的结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你在出发前赏脸参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请您务必让我出席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们结婚得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常都是年过二十才结婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我初次拿到这把枪时的感觉还要好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问费用是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有个让学徒将自己唤作「师傅」的超强女枪手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到处旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一头栽进纠纷当中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时而被人感谢 时而又被人憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这个女人的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫做「守林人」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我以前旅行时总是佩于腰际的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望让它再次出外旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意收下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我好好用它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么说不知道师傅的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅曾对我说过 将来要是有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要这么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为她担心你的安危呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人以前到底做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天过得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 我还有一个地方想要让你去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我最喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着终有一天 当我有自己的客人时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把这儿介绍给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺是我的第一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行时有没有痛苦的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你想放弃旅行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我大概也会继续旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为… 奇诺觉得旅行是自己非做不可的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我想要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将来想要继承父母的家业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为一个出色的旅馆经理和观光向导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你已经是个出色的向导了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两天我过得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 艾尔梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要了解更多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为一个杰出的向导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让无数的旅人造访我所出生的这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编织出众多永生难忘的美好回忆 令他们满载而归
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很了不起的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星辰无论何时何地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都毫无差别地点亮着世间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是和昨天同样的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却觉得今晚的星光更为温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱也试着去往别的地方仰望这片星空如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若樱你愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出外旅行也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以像奇诺那样四处游历
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再回到这里当向导也不迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这也是一种学习的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在这儿好好学习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为这儿最棒的向导
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久 不知会不会由于樱殷勤地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而让我们俩没事可干了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家跟谣言所说的截然不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然最初我很介怀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到中途我就不以为意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟睡过了头 你怎么了？奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生物钟是不是紊乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸袋中有树的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说获得拿着那颗种子迎接明日清晨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会成为下一个幸福的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 我就只有运气比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以收下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这不足以作为你替我带路的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一次都没取到过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直希望着有一天能拿到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 奇诺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奇诺替我拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 你差不多该出国了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否再待一、二天呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 你怎么了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉…有这样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要这么惊讶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在入国前说过只会待三天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行李在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果要在西去的途中露宿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好在山顶一带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山顶的更前方会有落石的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺 请你牢记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能在山顶的更前方露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是本国传统的户外食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和樱一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 这个也送你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我获得了非常美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们为我所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们告诉我们的地方 这里就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到奇诺会想待三天以上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很是惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好国家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱 我叫樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那个国家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火山灰和碎石在高温状态下喷涌而出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由山道高速流泻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火成碎屑流（Pyroclastic Flow）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简称「火碎流」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体中的血液会在一瞬间沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休克而死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连逃离的余地都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇诺是无能为力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「据学者的调查」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「得知火碎流将会袭击本国一事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大约是在一个月以前」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们只能在两条路中做出选择」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是要舍弃国家」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还是不舍弃」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「身为旅行者的你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一定会觉得我们的选择相当愚蠢吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但我们诞生于此」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不懂得其他的生存方式」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们并没有怨恨命运」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「而是选择在此度过余日」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这时我们惊觉」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们的国家在此之前都对旅人施以了极为不逊的态度」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这样下去 我们会以冷淡无情的形象」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「残存于人们的记忆中」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「讽刺的是」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「当我们洗心革面后」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「却再也没有旅人造访了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就当只剩下三天 大家都已绝望之时」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你们造访了我们的国家」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇诺 艾尔梅斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再一次感谢你们」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「此外 知晓这个事实的只有大人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你或许会认为我们很任性」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但那孩子就由我们带走了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太自以为是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…太自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论怎样 乘坐两个人是无法旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「致奇诺」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这是我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的内容呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)}「这个即便我拿着也没用」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)}「请不要忘了我们 ——樱」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:05.53,标题1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,290)\fad(500,200)}我不会终结我的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:11.18,标题1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(130,290)\fad(500,200)}终曲
